	color = { 0 0 0 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

e_Marklazine = {
	color = { 109 53 12 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Alekoae

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

	k_Mallhemeate = {
		color = { 66 113 34 }

				}

e_Morganargalous = {
	color = { 195 62 17 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Oepklazothrae

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

e_Goitanthos = {
	color = { 180 191 20 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Cololarisissa

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

	k_France = {
		color = { 0 128 255 }

		capital = c_Cololarisissa

		can_create = {

		}

e_Nymphgolita = {
	color = { 136 128 35 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Okamarnes

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

			NOT = {

e_Kelium = {
	color = { 50 50 50 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Orchogythessa

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

			NOT = {
			faith = {

		}

		if = {
			limit = {

			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

		}
